# Test API endpoints locally
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### API Root
GET http://localhost:8000/

### API Documentation
GET http://localhost:8000/docs

### Test CORS (check if v0.app can connect)
OPTIONS http://localhost:8000/codes
Origin: https://v0.app

### List Codes (add your API key)
GET http://localhost:8000/codes
# Authorization: Bearer your-api-key-here

### Test Action Processing
POST http://localhost:8000/actions/process
# Authorization: Bearer your-api-key-here

### Check Action Status  
GET http://localhost:8000/actions/status
# Authorization: Bearer your-api-key-here
